Psalm 70-1 <pb/><t><f>ⓐ</f> <f>ⓑ</f> Make haste, O God, to deliver me! </t><t>O LORD, make haste to help me!</t>
Psalm 70-2 <t>Let them be put to shame and confusion </t><t>who seek my life! </t><t>Let them be turned back and brought to dishonor </t><t>who delight in my hurt!</t>
Psalm 70-3 <t>Let them turn back because of their shame </t><t>who say, “Aha, Aha!” </t>
Psalm 70-4 <pb/><t>May all who seek you </t><t>rejoice and be glad in you! </t><t>May those who love your salvation </t><t>say evermore, “God is great!”</t>
Psalm 70-5 <t>But I am poor and needy; </t><t><f>ⓒ</f>hasten to me, O God! </t><t>You are my help and my deliverer; </t><t>O LORD, do not delay! </t>